verbose_text: While macrophages infected with STm lost UBE2L3, Casp1/4 -/- cells retained UBE2L3 protein (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G); the STmDeltaprgH mutant lacking the SPI-1 T3SS did not stimulate caspase-1 or deplete UBE2L3 (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY G).
evidence: STmDeltaprgH mutant lacking the SPI-1 T3SS did not stimulate caspase-1 or deplete UBE2L3
